0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 03, 2025</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104yth1665702550544.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/yth1665702550544.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/yth1665702550544.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"yth1665702550544\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Component Entity\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">A Component Entity is a Development Object that represents data that is owned by a Component. It is part of the Component’s structure and is maintained as part of the Component, although it may reference and inherit from a Modeled Entity.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"yth1665702550544__p_d94754e1_d94755e1_d94756e1\">A Component Entity that inherits from a Modeled Entity is\n      known as a <dfn class=\"term\">derived entity</dfn>.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"yth1665702550544__section_jxw_h5p_lwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d738670e57\">Characteristics</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"yth1665702550544__table_d10484e1_d10485e1_d10486e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"yth1665702550544__table_d10484e1_d10485e1_d10486e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Characteristics</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"yth1665702550544__table_d10484e1_d10485e1_d10486e1__entry__2\"></th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yth1665702550544__table_d10484e1_d10485e1_d10486e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Icon:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yth1665702550544__table_d10484e1_d10485e1_d10486e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\"><img alt=\"Icon\" class=\"image\" id=\"yth1665702550544__image_lnp_l5p_lwb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/component_entity.png?_LANG=enus\"/></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yth1665702550544__table_d10484e1_d10485e1_d10486e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Object type code:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yth1665702550544__table_d10484e1_d10485e1_d10486e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">ent</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yth1665702550544__table_d10484e1_d10485e1_d10486e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Main Development Object?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yth1665702550544__table_d10484e1_d10485e1_d10486e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">No</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yth1665702550544__table_d10484e1_d10485e1_d10486e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Part of:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yth1665702550544__table_d10484e1_d10485e1_d10486e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ifc1665702608950.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ifc1665702608950.html\" title=\"A Component is a Main Development Object that defines an executable part of an application. It defines the data structure used to access data, the layout (if applicable) used to present it, and the actions used to modify, validate, and store data.\">Component</a>, Component Entity, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xyt1665703024880.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xyt1665703024880.html\" title=\"A Derived Component Entity is a Development Object that references and inherits from a Modeled Entity. It has a Component or Modeled Component as parent object. It is used for the component's database I/O, data presentation, and inter-component communication.\">Derived Component Entity</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yth1665702550544__table_d10484e1_d10485e1_d10486e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Contains:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yth1665702550544__table_d10484e1_d10485e1_d10486e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Component Entity, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xyt1665703024880.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xyt1665703024880.html\" title=\"A Derived Component Entity is a Development Object that references and inherits from a Modeled Entity. It has a Component or Modeled Component as parent object. It is used for the component's database I/O, data presentation, and inter-component communication.\">Derived Component Entity</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zyj1665702550619.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zyj1665702550619.html\" title=\"A Component Field is a Development Object that represents a unit of data in a Component Entity.\">Component Field</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wyt1665702609153.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wyt1665702609153.html\" title=\"A Label is a Development Object that contains text that appears on a presentation component. Labels have properties, but most cannot be set dynamically.\">Label</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jgi1665702550212.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jgi1665702550212.html\" title=\"A Property is a named, typed attribute of Development Object that defines a characteristic or behavior of the object. Each property has a descriptive name, a literal name, a data type, and a value. If no value is specified, a default value may be used.\">Property</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cny1665702550298.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cny1665702550298.html\" title=\"A Code Container is a type of Property that holds code, such as ProcScript, JavaScript, or HTML. It can contain one or more code modules, such as triggers, operations, functions, or entries, or HTML for the layout.\">Code Container</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yth1665702550544__table_d10484e1_d10485e1_d10486e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Generalization:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yth1665702550544__table_d10484e1_d10485e1_d10486e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"uqv1665702561461.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/uqv1665702561461.html\" title=\"An Entity is an abstract data type that defines a logical data aggregation and its associated default characteristics and behavior. It may be mapped to a table in a DBMS, and is most frequently used to represent the application data, but it can also represent transient data, a collection of controls, or constant data.\">Entity</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yth1665702550544__table_d10484e1_d10485e1_d10486e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Specializations:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yth1665702550544__table_d10484e1_d10485e1_d10486e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xyt1665703024880.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xyt1665703024880.html\" title=\"A Derived Component Entity is a Development Object that references and inherits from a Modeled Entity. It has a Component or Modeled Component as parent object. It is used for the component's database I/O, data presentation, and inter-component communication.\">Derived Component Entity</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yth1665702550544__table_d10484e1_d10485e1_d10486e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Compilation Output:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yth1665702550544__table_d10484e1_d10485e1_d10486e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yth1665702550544__table_d10484e1_d10485e1_d10486e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">URI format:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yth1665702550544__table_d10484e1_d10485e1_d10486e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">cpt:<var class=\"keyword varname\">ComponentName</var>/ent:<var class=\"keyword varname\">EntityName</var>\n</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"yth1665702550544__section_vyv_n5p_lwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d738670e308\">Specialization</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"yth1665702550544__p_d94763e1_d94764e1_d94765e1\">Component Entity specializes Development Object and\n        Entity in the following ways:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"yth1665702550544__ul_v11_q5p_lwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"yth1665702550544__li_d37121e1_d37122e1_d37123e1\">It has a Component or a Component Entity as\n          parent.</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"yth1665702550544__li_d37124e1_d37125e1_d37126e1\">It can contain other Component Entities.</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"yth1665702550544__li_d37127e1_d37128e1_d37129e1\">It is created and maintained as part of the\n          Component.</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"yth1665702550544__section_s4m_r5p_lwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d738670e329\">Properties</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"yth1665702550544__p_d94778e1_d94779e1_d94780e1\">Properties defining the size, position, and repetition of\n        object frame in the layout of Form and Report components:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"yth1665702550544__ul_syd_55p_lwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"yth1665702550544__li_d37133e1_d37134e1_d37135e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mpr1665702587008.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mpr1665702587008.html\" title=\"Position of an object frame on a horizontal axis relative to its parent, excluding the border (if present); expressed as number of character cells.\">Left (xpos)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"yth1665702550544__li_d37136e1_d37137e1_d37138e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"aon1665702587081.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aon1665702587081.html\" title=\"Position of an object frame on a vertical axis relative to its parent, excluding the border (if present); expressed as number of character cells.\">Top (ypos)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"yth1665702550544__li_d37142e1_d37143e1_d37144e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"swp1665702587155.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/swp1665702587155.html\" title=\"Width of the object frame in the layout of a Form or Report, expressed in character cells, excluding the border (if present).\">Width (xsize)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"yth1665702550544__li_d37139e1_d37140e1_d37141e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"nai1665703058765.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nai1665703058765.html\" title=\"Height of the object frame in the layout of a Form or Report, expressed in character cells, excluding the border (if present).\">Height (ysize)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"yth1665702550544__li_d37145e1_d37146e1_d37147e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mok1665702703254.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mok1665702703254.html\" title=\"The number of times the entity or area frame is repeated horizontally in a Form or Report. The minimum (and default) is 1.\">Horizontal Repetition</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"yth1665702550544__li_d37148e1_d37149e1_d37150e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fmf1665702703323.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fmf1665702703323.html\" title=\"The number of times the entity or area frame is repeated vertically in a Form or Report. The minimum (and default) is 1.\">Vertical Repetition</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"yth1665702550544__li_d37151e1_d37152e1_d37153e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dmh1665702703396.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dmh1665702703396.html\" title=\"Specifies whether an entity scrollbar is displayed, and its position. Valid values are Automatic (default), No, Yes, Top, Bottom, Left, Right.\">Scrollbar</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"yth1665702550544__li_d37154e1_d37155e1_d37156e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gmd1665702587249.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gmd1665702587249.html\" title=\"This property determines whether a border is displayed around the area frame, entity or occurrence frame, or field. It is set from the context menu in the form canvas.\">Border</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"yth1665702550544__li_d37157e1_d37158e1_d37159e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wwg1665702587409.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wwg1665702587409.html\" title=\"Code that identifies a Uniface index color, which represents a combination of background and foreground colors. Applicable only to Form components. Deprecated.\">Index Color</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3617251\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3617251\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Component Entity Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 03, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Component Entity A Component Entity is a Development Object that represents data that is owned by a Component. It is part of the Component’s structure and is maintained as part of the Component, although it may reference and inherit from a Modeled Entity. A Component Entity that inherits from a Modeled Entity is known as a derived entity . Characteristics Characteristics Icon: Object type code: ent Main Development Object? No Part of: Component , Component Entity, Derived Component Entity Contains: Component Entity, Derived Component Entity , Component Field , Label , Property , Code Container Generalization: Entity Specializations: Derived Component Entity Compilation Output: — URI format: cpt: ComponentName /ent: EntityName Specialization Component Entity specializes Development Object and Entity in the following ways: It has a Component or a Component Entity as parent. It can contain other Component Entities. It is created and maintained as part of the Component. Properties Properties defining the size, position, and repetition of object frame in the layout of Form and Report components: Left (xpos) Top (ypos) Width (xsize) Height (ysize) Horizontal Repetition Vertical Repetition Scrollbar Border Index Color Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}